---
import { site } from '../config';
import '../styles/products.css';
const { local, tribal, global: globalProduct } = site.products;
---
<section class="platforms" id="products">
  <div class="platforms-head">
    <span class="kicker">§ 02 &nbsp;·&nbsp; The three platforms</span>
    <h2 class="display platforms-display">One parent.<br>Three economies. <em>One method.</em></h2>
    <p class="lede platforms-lede">
      Lumecon Inc. is the parent brand. Each platform inherits the same modeling backbone &mdash; transparent multipliers, auditable assumptions, exportable provenance &mdash; and then bends the intake, the geography, and the language to the economy it serves.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="platforms-grid">
    <a class="platform platform--local" href={local.url}>
      <header class="platform__head">
        <span class="platform__num mono">01</span>
        <span class="platform__tag mono">Local</span>
      </header>
      <h3 class="platform__name">Local Economic<br>Impact</h3>
      <div class="platform__url mono">{local.domain}</div>
      <p class="platform__desc">Rigorous economic and policy analysis for US municipal governments, enterprises, nonprofits, and economic development organizations &mdash; without the cost or complexity of traditional tools.</p>
      <footer class="platform__foot">
        <span class="platform__status mono">{local.status}</span>
        <span class="platform__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </footer>
      <svg class="platform__line" viewBox="0 0 320 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M0 60 C 60 30, 120 70, 180 40 S 280 30, 320 50" />
      </svg>
    </a>

    <a class="platform platform--tribal" href={tribal.url}>
      <header class="platform__head">
        <span class="platform__num mono">02</span>
        <span class="platform__tag mono">Tribal</span>
      </header>
      <h3 class="platform__name">Tribal Economic<br>Impact</h3>
      <div class="platform__url mono">{tribal.domain}</div>
      <p class="platform__desc">Built for economies that don&rsquo;t fit standard assumptions. Designed from day one for tribes, Alaska Native Corporations, Native Hawaiian Organizations, and reservation economies &mdash; with Indigenous data sovereignty baked in.</p>
      <footer class="platform__foot">
        <span class="platform__status mono">{tribal.status}</span>
        <span class="platform__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </footer>
      <svg class="platform__line" viewBox="0 0 320 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M0 50 C 80 70, 140 20, 200 50 S 280 60, 320 30" />
      </svg>
    </a>

    <a class="platform platform--global" href={globalProduct.url}>
      <header class="platform__head">
        <span class="platform__num mono">03</span>
        <span class="platform__tag mono">Global</span>
      </header>
      <h3 class="platform__name">Global Economic<br>Impact</h3>
      <div class="platform__url mono">{globalProduct.domain}</div>
      <p class="platform__desc">The same core modeling framework, applied across borders &mdash; supporting cross-border and multiregional analysis for multinationals, NGOs, and governments. Comparable methods, comparable results.</p>
      <footer class="platform__foot">
        <span class="platform__status mono">{globalProduct.status}</span>
        <span class="platform__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </footer>
      <svg class="platform__line" viewBox="0 0 320 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M0 40 C 70 60, 130 20, 200 35 S 280 70, 320 40" />
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
